replies.body:
Broporo ooooon duty! {{summoner:31}} 

Even if you can't get into the e-mail that you used to create your League account, we can still get your password recovered. Reach out to us through our [**Account Recovery Form**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new?ticket_form_id=72416), and we'll be able to go over everything for you there.

Be sure to stay signed out when you fill out that form, and you'll be back on the Rift in no time ^_^!
